## Critical Path

The longest dependency chain to NavCom's core identity:

```
00-01 Design System ──→ (unblocks 05-06 Accessibility)
00-04 E2E Tests    ──→ (safety net for everything)

01-01 Mode Store   ──→ 01-02 Sidebar ──→ 01-03 Comms View ──→ 03-01 Message Types
                    ╰→ 01-07 Tab Bar                        ╰→ 05-01 Virtualization
                    ╰→ 01-04 Map View ──→ 03-03 Linking ──→ 04-01 Layers

02-01 PQC Wiring   ──→ 02-02 Key UI ──→ 05-05 Key Storage ──→ 06-03 Trust
                    ╰→ 05-03 Offline Queue                    ╰→ 06-02 Mesh
```

**Shortest path to "NavCom feels like NavCom"**: 01-01 → 01-07 → 01-02 → 01-03 (4 tasks, ~450 lines)

**Shortest path to "real encryption"**: 02-01 → 02-02 (2 tasks, already have 556 tests passing)

